Class CustomCompositeBaseRT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.fieldType.runtime.base.AbstractFieldTypeRT

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICustomFieldTypeRT, IFieldTypeRT, ILucene
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomSelectParentChildGrandchildRT, CustomSelectParentChildrenRT, CustomSelectParentChildRT

    public abstract class CustomCompositeBaseRT
extends AbstractFieldTypeRT
implements ICustomFieldTypeRT
    A custom composite field is a composite of other custom single fields It is itself a CustomFieldTypeRT
